    17	This proposal is the response to `SAFETY_CASE.md` §5's open numeric register and to review
    18	finding **F9** (U-T1), which routed the tracker detection-threshold false-alarm analysis here
    19	(`DECISIONS.md` D36). It turns each `[UNVERIFIED]` authority-contract parameter into a
