    22	fields**: it includes the six protection limits, `t_lease`/`t_dr`/`t_eph`, the caution
    23	band/revoke/dwells/`T_ack`, **and the per-source freshness deadlines** (§2.4) — the last of
    24	which are named in the fail-closed register but are **absent from `AuthorityParams` and its
